ags-simple-file.ags-sf-config:
[generic] autosave-thread=false simple-file=true disable-feature=experimental engine-mode=performance
[thread] model=super-threaded super-threaded-scope=audio lock-global=ags-thread lock-parent=ags-recycling-thread max-precision=250
[soundcard-0] backend=pulse device=ags-pulse-devout-0 pcm-channels=2 samplerate=48000 buffer-size=512 use-cache=true cache-buffer-size=4096 format=16
[recall] auto-sense=true
